      </div>
      <div style="flex: 1; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #ececec; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px;">
        <span style="color: #888888; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase;">Entrées (Ce mois)</span>
        <div style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 8px; color: #10b981;">+3.5 <span style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500;">T</span></div>
      </div>
      <div style="flex: 1; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #ececec; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px;">
        <span style="color: #888888; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase;">Alertes Seuil Critique</span>
        <div style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 8px; color: #df1c1c;">2 Articles</div>
      </div>
    </div>

